wiki.summary: “Late at Night” is a melodic ballad from Compton native Roddy Ricch that sees him sing about passionate love for his significant other, with Mustard producing the smooth-flowing beat. Roddy released a snippet on Twitter on May 10, 2021, with the single-emoji caption alluding to the track potentially being the next single from his expected trilogy-ending mixtape, Feed Tha Streets III. On May 25, he went back on the platform to confirm that the track would be released on June 4 Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: “Late at Night” is a melodic ballad from Compton native Roddy Ricch that sees him sing about passionate love for his significant other, with Mustard producing the smooth-flowing beat. Roddy released a snippet on Twitter on May 10, 2021, with the single-emoji caption alluding to the track potentially being the next single from his expected trilogy-ending mixtape, Feed Tha Streets III. On May 25, he went back on the platform to confirm that the track would be released on June 4, dropping alongside its accompanying “Thriller”-inspired music video. Read more on Last.fm.
